Text: Believe me when i say im trying to be as nice as possible about this. Don't post that kind of shit around here! How old r u... 12? Thats ridiculous. go post that on youtube or some other place that idiots can congregate and simultaneously lower one anothers IQ. We dont need people like that in our community. If anyone thinks im out of line you can let me know, but its stuff like that that really makes me angry.
